prompt:

Nurse: Hi, this is Rachel calling from O'Connor Hospital. I'm an AI on a recorded line. Is this Timoteo Valenzuela?

Patient: Yeah. That's me.

Nurse: Great, Mr. Valenzuela. I'm calling about your upcoming colonoscopy on August 13th at 9:00 AM. Is this a good time to talk?

responses.gpt4: Excellent, thank you for taking the time. I hope your day has been treating you well. Before diving, how have you been feeling in general as your procedure approaches?
responses.our_model: Thank you, Mr. Valenzuela. I hope your day is going well so far. How are you feeling about your upcoming procedure?
